02:11.833 --> 02:14.375
<i>And can you get some ice</i>
<i>from the 24-hour store?</i>

02:14.458 --> 02:16.791
<i>Your buddy can't do without</i>
<i>his gin and tonic.</i>

02:16.875 --> 02:18.291
