02:18.375 --> 02:20.958
<i>Go on, don't be long. Big kiss.</i>

02:21.416 --> 02:22.833
See you soon. Big kiss.

02:33.000 --> 02:34.333
That's it, Jon. Let's go.

02:34.416 --> 02:35.833
Thirty-two minutes late.

02:35.916 --> 02:37.875
Sorry. I'll tell you later. Go.

02:37.958 --> 02:39.708
I need some ice
from the 24-hour store.

02:40.875 --> 02:41.750
And champagne.

02:59.125 --> 03:01.291
No shit. You're going to ask her?

03:03.250 --> 03:04.291
Tonight?

03:04.375 --> 03:05.750
Sure, with you there.

03:06.833 --> 03:10.666
Fuck, no. I'll tell her we're spending
the weekend in Paris.

03:10.833 --> 03:12.041
That's great. Paris.

03:12.416 --> 03:14.583
Yes. I'll propose to her in Paris.

03:14.666 --> 03:15.583
She'll love it.

03:16.500 --> 03:18.708
I'm happy for you. For both of you.

03:18.791 --> 03:19.625
I know.

03:23.125 --> 03:25.333
And you know who's going to be
my best man?

03:25.416 --> 03:28.375
-If she says yes.
-Shit, man. Can you imagine?

03:28.500 --> 03:31.958
Kneeling under the Eiffel Tower like:
"Will you marry me?"

03:32.166 --> 03:33.750
"Well, no.

03:34.458 --> 03:35.916
Fuck off!"

03:36.500 --> 03:37.333
